{"tid":2089417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗爭進化］低風險 畫面靚 邊到都做到既抗爭","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T16:00:59.000Z","uid":323296,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85518946ebb17a52f2cc13dc4f044e3752da185b","tid":2089417,"uid":323296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"首先多謝今日出來咁多位手足 <br />\n係咁多佈陣既情況下都咁多人出 真係好感動<br />\n但反思宜加運動既去向 可以話係困難重重<br />\n首先要再聚大量人既成本同難度都好高<br />\n但宜加好需要向各方面展示大家心入面團火係未熄<br />\n所以我地需要一個 低門檻 低成本 容易做既抗爭模式<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拍手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足可以係唔同場合用同一個節奏拍手，多人既時候畫面可以好震撼。而且唔需要聚到好埋都可以做到。當然你可以話要拉唔洗理由，但拍手既動機好含糊，成本比叫口號低得多。最重要係邊到都得，可以係街，商場，甚至可以騎劫大型活動 （有咩活動自己諗）。其實外國都已經有過呢類抗爭<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.theatlantic.com/amp/article/242271/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.theatlantic.com%2Famp%2Farticle%2F242271%2F&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9THxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=44608924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.theatlantic.com/amp/article/242271/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家諗下做唔做得過，集思廣益"},{"pid":"f6daeddc52f611a17725577ea2f41f6ea5ad219a","tid":2089417,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ec52ce0a3c241359f7091472b266f826938af3","tid":2089417,"uid":323296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"P牌仔 大家幫推"},{"pid":"ecaa459dde579b86653433901cf032626ad553b9","tid":2089417,"uid":323876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:58:50.000Z","msg":"唱聖詩"},{"pid":"74d186a035ace42530ec76c19bd2c56901c0ee96","tid":2089417,"uid":91199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PVq0MrmezpI\" data-sr-url=\"h